Package reversiblegate.mctgate

Enum Class GateControl

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GateControl>
reversiblegate.mctgate.GateControl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<GateControl>, Constable
public enum GateControl extends Enum<GateControl>
It is an enum representing three possible inputs of a MCT gate. It also contains methods to convert integer value to its equivalent enum constants.
Author:
AKASH
